    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▸ <strong>Bilibili</strong> — @雪风樱制作组</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▸ <strong>微博</strong> — @苍蓝恋诗-雪风樱制作组</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>▸ Q群①：</strong>290116525（RING·雪风樱制作组）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>    Q群②：</strong>141932215（天启市选民热线）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223430/extras/ab2a2da5c8d4705713d0e780c20d7479.avif?t=1760115733\" width=615 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>                                           “——欢迎来到天启，星球最后的乐土。”</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223430/extras/c4a9289155a8c008935583c52e87db1c.webp?t=1760115733\" width=185 height=50 /></span>  </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  你回到了这座城市——星球最后的乐土，奇迹之都。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  在久违的蓝天与日常中来一场新生活！认识新的朋友，与身怀秘密的少女们相遇，结识羁绊与爱恋。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  夏日庆典、大异灾、永不凋零之花、原初的小世界……</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  在一次次的奇妙经历中，发掘城市、少女与你自身的秘密。这个八月，与她一同行至星之尽头。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223430/extras/02729bb6b960a77d916a4a74551b2619.webp?t=1760115733\" width=185 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >      自天启市建立已经过去了38年。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223430/extras/81b68d09e45c5d64eb8f3d3399f3d6ce.avif?t=1760115733\" width=500 height=315 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >      这座城市并非一开始便如人们口中的那样，“乐土”、“最后之城”、“奇迹之都”……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >      曾经，世界上有森林、国度、战争……那是辉煌的年代，这座城市的建立也不过新增一隅之所。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >      但在一场劫难过后，大地衰败，异灾横行。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >      数十年的时光流逝，在这期间，繁华的国度倾倒、星辰的地表失色，唯有这座城市，仍旧如初。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >      不知原因的人们或是在城内的安宁中祈祷它的永驻，或是在城外的疯狂中诅咒它的毁塌，亦或是在生命消逝前，彼此一同凝望着它。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >      ……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >      天启38年，8月。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >      离开这座城市的一年后，你又回到了这里。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223430/extras/e98b69a84fd158994b24f66ac3064ab6.webp?t=1760115733\" width=185 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223430/extras/285f3191fc8c9b6c2833decc48901859.avif?t=1760115733\" width=400 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>「 摩莉甘，我对她怀有最多的……还是愧疚之情吧。直至如今，她的生命之舟还尚未启航 」</i></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>RUNO / 摩莉甘·朱诺</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在纯白之庭中沉睡的迷之少女，似乎有着某种奇特的能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >平日里十分天然，容易冒出奇奇怪怪的跳脱思路，在危急关头会显露出认真的一面。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被主人公唤醒后与其同居，爱读童话课本、喜欢阅览世界的过去。认为自己的诞生是一种使命。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223430/extras/80ee0298d91221f6433d41e9edc2536d.avif?t=1760115733\" width=394 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>「 天鹅绒里的恶魔，怀揣一颗秘密的心 」</i></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>LUNA / 露娜·埃斯特雷亚</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >望月高校新一届学生会长，月面财团千金，异灾治理委托的对接人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >性格慵懒，足够有空的话能够在办公室面对一整天电脑。心如静水流深，令人捉摸不透。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223430/extras/75b0f6e24c3c6dbbf7c43a140f304bbe.avif?t=1760115733\" width=400 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>「 一朵永恒的花，理应自己埋葬自己 」</i></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>LILY / 莉莉斯·朱诺</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >罕有情绪波动的少女，肤色苍白，身上环绕着绷带与荆棘状的不明物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 白天在安静的地带与小动物作伴，夜晚则在大森林深处独自徘徊。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223430/extras/7d400ec8c1b549a1aa6ac202574f4237.avif?t=1760115733\" width=400 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>「 谁将朱墨染夏枫？自有萱花醉晚风 」</i></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CHUNXUAN / 椿萱</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >夏恒的青梅竹马，天启市最高学府『天府』的预招生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >平日里性格温婉，心情好时会故意逗弄亲近的人，但实际上性格很倔。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身处高中毕业后的漫长暑假，准备着一场特殊的夏日庆典。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
